  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<b>白兰树</b><br/>\n<br/>\r\n我有几棵白兰树<br/>\r\n临夏秋中花如簇<br/>\r\n盛时芬芳播雨露<br/>\r\n每过回头依芯嗅<br/>\r\n轻冻爆热皆摧折<br/>\r\n过湿过干都消瘦<br/>\r\n暮霭推窗浓扑入<br/>\r\n常伴此香飘碎梦。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n—— 晨起餐后院中散步偶得<br/>\n<br/>\r\n见我英文白兰树小介绍： <a href=\"url/link/aHR0cDovL2ZyYWdyYW50Zmxvd2Vycy5uZXQvbWljaGVsaWFhbGJhL21pY2hlbGlhYWxiYS5odG1s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://fragrantflowers.net/micheliaalba/micheliaalba.html\">http://fragrantflowers.net/micheliaalba/micheliaalba.html</a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9hT2RiNzdFLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/aOdb77E.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/aOdb77E.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aOdb77E.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS85VEw3alpmLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/9TL7jZf.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9TL7jZf.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9TL7jZf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
